getPowerRate

public long getPowerRate()
Description copied from interface: PowerRate
Returns the power rate of the device in mW. A negative value indicates discharging whereas a positive value indicates charging (typically discharging should be the case during energy testing).

Returns:
The power rate of the battery device in mW.
